reviews.text: Great place for hot pot especially for a group. Service is good. It's a one hour buffet and they offer lots of good food. Fresh meat like chicken and beef and pork and different kinds of vegetables. Drinks is also unlimited like soft drinks, juices and beers. Desserts are also available such as ice cream and frozen yogurt. You can also choose any toppings. Price is okay and I probably recommend this restaurant.
